                <p>-ilk muhalif&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;&#39; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ahrar
                    partisi</p>

                <p>-En g&uuml;&ccedil;l&uuml; muhalif parti H&uuml;rriyet ve İtilaf partisi</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

